{"tid":2512048,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"變種病毒︱外傭團體批政府歧視及種族主義 將尋求法律意見 促羅致光就「可以唔嚟」言論道歉","createTime":"2021-05-01T11:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T11:50:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"72e612752a254e61927aeba21466ac8c04c58b44","tid":2512048,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:22:09.000Z","msg":"政府昨（4月30日）突然要求全港37萬名外傭強制檢測，並規定續約時必須接種疫苗，勞工及福利局局長羅致光更表明，外傭可選擇不來港工作。多個外傭團體今日（1日）舉行聯合記者會，批評港府將外傭污名化，標籤為變種病毒來源，「完全係歧視同種族主義」。團體促政府審議政策，並要求羅致光收回帶侮辱性的言論及向外傭道歉，亦有代表稱不認同港府硬性規外傭接種疫苗成工作簽證條件，會就新政策尋求法律意見。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210501/VOH5GLJNPVCFVOS27XNHKTTVK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210501%2FVOH5GLJNPVCFVOS27XNHKTTVK4%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNm%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=3789ccaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210501%2FVOH5GLJNPVCFVOS27XNHKTTVK4%2F&h=fff890e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210501/VOH5GLJNPVCFVOS27XNHKTTVK4/</a>"},{"pid":"5d437030fa8068dd3bb21868fe000b78a78bb390","tid":2512048,"uid":134227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國安法"},{"pid":"0390f53dfe87fa9b4a4590393aad3222b75387de","tid":2512048,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"Btw 菲律賓解ban咗陶傑未"},{"pid":"2a550c48248700cfaa54544e6366de2ad333ceb8","tid":2512048,"uid":1069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:24:11.000Z","msg":"國安法拉人"},{"pid":"7c00673a70eab1e115fb83ac4ed767d994df6298","tid":2512048,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:50:01.000Z","msg":"出國做工人，有乜尊嚴可言"}]}